<div id="review_1622666289" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1622666289" />
    <a title="Mike Perry" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44300857-mike-perry"><img alt="Mike Perry" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1435364587p2/44300857.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1622666289?book_show_action=true">Apr 27, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mike Perry" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mike Perry" href="/user/show/44300857-mike-perry">Mike Perry</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/28508648-confederates">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1622666289" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7643522346860525281"><strong>As good as fiction can be about this awful war, particularly the common men fighting a useless war they never understood. </strong><br/><br/>On a par with All Quiet on the Western Front. Beautiful and sad and awful. No sense of glory., no sense of the worth of the pitiful cause. But a heartfelt study of the best and worst of each of us caught <br/>in an insane river of destructio</span>

          </span>
        </div>


